{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834670/extras/Descriptio.jpg?t=1736292299\" /><br><br>In the aftermath of a devastating world war, nations unleashed both nuclear and biological weapons, turning the world into a wasteland. The fallout from the biological warfare transformed survivors into zombie-like creatures known as the Fibers. Humanity now clings to survival in isolated pockets, desperately searching for a cure to the deadly virus that morphs them into Fibers. In this post-apocalyptic world, our protagonist emerges as a beacon of hope, venturing into the heart of the origin of the virus. His mission: to find a cure, humanity's last chance against the encroaching darkness. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834670/extras/movement.gif?t=1736292299\" /><br><br>Immerse yourself in an open-world action/horror experience where survival is paramount. Navigate through stunning and diverse locations while mastering stealth, utilizing a variety of melee and ranged weapons, gadgets, and grenade types. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834670/extras/weather.gif?t=1736292299\" /><br><br>Encounter relentless, smart AI zombies as you adapt to the dynamic time of day and weather system. Explore the world with a complex movement system, including vaulting, ziplining, swimming, and climbing. Employ advanced tools like drones and binoculars to scout and strategize. It's your fight for survival in a world gone mad.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834670/extras/finisher.gif?t=1736292299\" /><br><br>Special Credits: pixabay, Renafox &amp; Jonathan Bogart","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2834670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736292299","background_raw